cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  C4B-NbS-Pipeline: Open-source data ingestion pipeline for Copernicus
  Sentinel-1/2 imagery integration with IoT environmental sensor streams
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file.
