repository-code: https://github.com/cloud4business/c4b-nbs-pipeline
url: https://www.cloud4business.it
abstract: >-
  A modular, open-source Python framework for ingesting, harmonising, and
  integrating Copernicus Sentinel-1/2 satellite imagery with in-situ IoT
  environmental sensor streams (LoRaWAN, MQTT) for evidence-based assessment
  of Nature-Based Solutions. Designed for on-premise deployment to ensure
  digital sovereignty over environmental data.
